&lt;Ecolab Co> of the United States signeda contract with North China Industrial Co to set up the firstSino-U.S. Joint venture in China to make rinsing agents, theNew China News Agency said.     It said total investment in the new venture, &lt;EcolabChemical Industrial Co>, is 2.4 mln dlrs. It said the venturewill be based in Shanghai and produce agents for use in hotelsand industries.    It gave no further details. REUTER&#3;